    "These models have been trained on extensive corpora and possess the ability to execute specific tasks without the need for additional training or hard coding [12].",
    "They are invoked and controlled simply by providing a natural language prompt.",
    "The degree to which LLMs understand the tasks depends largely on the prompts provided by users.The capabilities of LLMs have various implications for network protocols.",
    "Network protocols are implemented in accordance with the RFCs, which are written in natural language and available online.",
    "Since LLMs are pre-trained on billions of internet samples, they should be capable of understanding RFCs as well."
  ],
